com.mhealthatlas.apps.dto.NewIosAppInfoDto

Packages that use NewIosAppInfoDto 
Package Description
com.mhealthatlas.apps.command
com.mhealthatlas.apps.command is a group of services which only mutate data but have not advanced query functionalities.
com.mhealthatlas.apps.controller
com.mhealthatlas.apps.controller is a group of REST API controllers in the application service.
Each class ending with the QueryController prefix provides GET API endpoints for quering application information.
Each class ending with the CommandController prefix provides POST and DELETE API endpoints for mutating the application information state.
